            <h1> </h1>

            <h3 style="color: coral">Why rent with CarRent.com?</h3>
            <p>
                Of course, you can check the internet for the rates of every single car
                company to get the best value for your price. But we have three reasons, why you should consider booking with us:
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li>Compare great rates easily</li>
                <li> Big savings for smart customers </li>
                <li> Best rental cars in the United States and worldwide</li>
            </ul>
